sources.title: Frenzy
sources.description: Title: Frenzy Summary: A seance is held to discover the whereabouts, and the killer, of a sculptor's wife. Directed by: Vernon Sewell Actors: Derrick De Marney, Frederick Valk, Beresford Egan Production Company: British National Films Release Date: 19 July 1946 (USA) Aspect Ratio: 1.37 : 1 A seance is held to discover the whereabouts, and the killer, of a sculptor's wife.
